  "id": "CHAR_severin_arkell",
  "label": "Severin Arkell",
  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered, middle-aged human, marked by the thick forearms and squared hands of long service behind a bar. Brown eyes sit beneath a heavy brow, and brown hair is kept in a short, practical cut that leaves the face unobstructed. Bronze skin bears permanent heat-darkening across the knuckles and wrists, consistent with years of handling scalding vessels and harsh cleansers. A blunt nose and firm jawline give the features a sturdy, workmanlike cast.",
